---

## Installation

```cmd
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

On first run, YOLOv8 model weights (`yolov8s-seg.pt`) are downloaded automatically. An internet connection is required for the first run only.

---

## Usage

### Run full pipeline
```cmd
python pipeline.py --video input_video.mp4
```

### Test individual stages
```cmd
# Test YOLO detection on a single image
python stage1_detection.py --input frame_25.jpg

# Test feature extraction on a single image
python stage3_features.py --input frame_25.jpg

# Test database query with manual input
python stage4_db_query.py --color brown --w1 210 --h1 180 --h2 90

# Test task manager with a dummy new dog
python stage5_task_manager.py --dog_id TEST-001 --color brown --w1 200 --h1 170 --h2 85
```

